Layout fact: the source put a line break inside the opening tag, so the
attribute list is block-formatted (one attr per line, `>` alone). The formatter
preserves that even though the whole element fits on one line — the opening-tag
symmetry of ChildrenMultiline. The opening-tag break propagates to the children.

-- input.gsx --
package p

component C() {
	<a
		href="/help"
		class="text-blue-600"
	>?</a>
}
-- fmt.golden --
package p

component C() {
	<a
		href="/help"
		class="text-blue-600"
	>
		?
	</a>
}
